點解佢仲要講到好似係我錯咁 <br />\n係我唔理佢 唔搵佢<br />\n佢hea覆我時 我要搵野講 <br />\n佢hea得我多 愛因斯坦都諗唔到話題講啦"},{"pid":"0d12e22928417946b5375df0397c8be1480ade79","tid":433591,"uid":150680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"上莊唔忙幾時忙？唔通真係讀書咩"},{"pid":"9f8c0d72e654ba566127af9943c95bdc1171d397","tid":433591,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"上莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 898"},{"pid":"0c899ffb09d8d34c0b8a5ebae6b22c85e40d9d90","tid":433591,"uid":66076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"既然咁多不滿，對方又冷淡就分手啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對方都冇心維繫段關係，點做都嘥氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8e3dd34c75e959a5df08fc20a3c63a39b37e2c","tid":433591,"uid":151564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"我咪因為咁最後散左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ab9085fe44333d915ebad3fedeadb11c34f206","tid":433591,"uid":100135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢住天水圍 我住柴灣<br />\n898 LA</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人就唔介意啦<br />\n利申 同男朋友一個上水一個九龍灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1320a5e55400719db2f72482e4b03af4432f3fff","tid":433591,"uid":100135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"有拖拍仲上乜莊<br />\n曾經有一個男朋友因為上莊上到每個留得一日比我<br />\n我個陣ON99咁信佢真係忙 最後原來識咗個同莊嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話覺得自己陪唔到我所以分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6624b8cb56dba95bbf6b805dd6bd53f7a63f871","tid":433591,"uid":79382,"like":